item.title: About Me
item.description: Hi I am Caden and I like bread. I am currently working as web man for UBC Web Services. I love to code and learn new things. I am passionate about technology and I am always looking for new opportunities to learn and grow. I am currently working on a few side projects and I am always looking for new ideas to work on. If you have any questions or would like to get in touch, feel free to reach out to me.
